OL,3,CIncreasing gender pay gap for head
OL,4,Cteachers ` report
OL,6,FThe gender pay gap for head teachers
OL,7,Fhas widened to the worst level in up
OL,8,Fto 13 years, new research suggests.
OL,10,FSchool leaders' union NAHT said the
OL,11,Faverage pay gap between male and
OL,12,Ffemale head teachers was more than
OL,13,F#8,600 a year after increasing by
OL,14,Falmost 6% in 2023/24 compared to 2022/
OL,15,F23.
OL,17,FFor secondary heads, women earned
OL,18,Falmost #5,000 a year less on average
OL,19,Fthan men, which the union said was the
OL,20,Fbiggest gap for the last 13 years.
