OL,6,FGeneral secretary Paul Whiteman said:
OL,7,F"The gender pay gap matters. Over the
OL,8,Fcourse of a decades-long career a
OL,9,Fsmall disparity can amount to a large
OL,10,Fdifference in overall earnings, with
OL,11,Fmajor implications not only for an
OL,12,Findividual's salary, but also their
OL,13,Fpension rights and entitlements.
