OL,6,F"We have seen a major erosion of
OL,7,Fschool leaders' pay over the last
OL,8,Fdecade, but for women there has been a
OL,9,F'double hit' that must be tackled. The
OL,10,Fgender pay gap plagues every part of
OL,11,Fthe education sector, but for some
OL,12,Fareas of leadership it has now grown
OL,13,Fso wide that it is a chasm.
OL,15,F"This is especially outrageous in a
OL,16,Fprofession with a majority of women
OL,17,Fworkers.
